title: Jennifer Mello, LICSW – Certified trauma therapy in Plymouth, MA
content_sample: When I started my practice, at the root of everything I did, I held my clients in mind. Not only is this space a way for me to introduce myself to you, its also FOR you. I hope you find a sense of peace, belonging, and guidance if that is what you seek. Please feel free to check out my resources page with some links that you may find helpful, and don’t hesitate to reach out should you decide you’d like to connect.
